.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚市仲好意思收加一，食垃圾都五十蚊餐。</blockquote><br />\n宵夜唔差喎Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無食過晚市"},{"pid":"95f40152b75e26956b8cb6f2ef93ecd62401001d","tid":226453,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"以前真係幾抵食<br />\n而家真係拎去餵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f25f71d4852eea66f4502151bdcd610bb0fad7d","tid":226453,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2691b32974bc5d25d35a62e0d2b7bc6b0e65f1","tid":226453,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d28fe7e619eb3f0e4cdc1df035139da72ea04a","tid":226453,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"劣就劣啲，但飽肚嘅"},{"pid":"b5db00538aaf88091894d8e1e0e36b09a80a79f7","tid":226453,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打住附近?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6472a5bb8df529abefbdd99e4a50bb55f6a3cb","tid":226453,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T18:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打住附近?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif